    <texts>
      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">The Captain is about to arrive in the port of a high-risk country. What measures should the Captain take to prevent corruption risks in the port?</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" delay="0" crct="64" align="left">Post anti-corruption signs at the gangway and in the office so they are clearly visible for visitors</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" delay="0" crct="99" align="left">Double-check all documentation in advance, have all the documents ready and in order to present</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" delay="0" crct="32" align="left">Make sure to ask the agent about relevant local requirements and comply with them</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" delay="0" crct="80" align="left">All of the above</txt>
